RoSync - Customize Your Roblox Experience

Last Updated: December 24 , 2024

RoSync is a powerful extension designed to enhance your Roblox browsing experience by giving you control over specific page elements. With RoSync, you can easily toggle the visibility of round profile pictures, banners, and enable or disable additional features such as RoPro support. The extension remembers your preferences across sessions, ensuring your settings are automatically applied when you return.

Features:

Toggle Round Profile Pictures
Hide or display round profile pictures with a simple click. Perfect for users who prefer a more streamlined view or wish to focus on other content without distractions.

Manage Banner Visibility
Effortlessly show or hide banners on Roblox pages based on your preferences, giving you more control over your browsing experience.

Persistent Preferences
RoSync saves your preferences in local storage, ensuring that your settings are preserved across browsing sessions without needing to reapply them every time.

RoPro Support
Enable or disable support for the RoPro extension, integrating additional features when enabled. RoSync seamlessly works with RoPro to customize your Roblox experience even further.

Customize your Roblox browsing experience today with RoSync!
